{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.1","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:1","prev_osis_id":"Isa.053.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le bonheur qui attend Isra\u00ebl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. (Ga 4:22-27. \u00c9s 49:14-23.) (J\u00e9 29:10-14; 32:36-42.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    R\u00e9jouis-toi, st\u00e9rile, toi qui n\u2019enfantes plus!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Fais \u00e9clater ton all\u00e9gresse et ta joie, toi qui n\u2019as plus de douleurs!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car les fils de la d\u00e9laiss\u00e9e seront plus nombreux<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Que les fils de celle qui est mari\u00e9e, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.2","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.53.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 53:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.53.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.2","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:2","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>\u00c9largis l\u2019espace de ta tente;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qu\u2019on d\u00e9ploie les couvertures de ta demeure:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ne retiens pas!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Allonge tes cordages,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et affermis tes pieux!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.3","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.1","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.3","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:3","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Car tu te r\u00e9pandras \u00e0 droite et \u00e0 gauche;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ta post\u00e9rit\u00e9 envahira des nations,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et peuplera des villes d\u00e9sertes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.4","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.2","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.4","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:4","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Ne crains pas, car tu ne seras point confondue;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ne rougis pas, car tu ne seras pas d\u00e9shonor\u00e9e;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais tu oublieras la honte de ta jeunesse,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et tu ne te souviendras plus de l\u2019opprobre de ton veuvage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.5","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.3","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.5","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:5","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Car ton cr\u00e9ateur est ton \u00e9poux:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u2019\u00c9ternel des arm\u00e9es est son nom;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ton r\u00e9dempteur est le Saint d\u2019Isra\u00ebl:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il se nomme Dieu de toute la terre;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.6","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.4","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.6","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:6","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Car l\u2019\u00c9ternel te rappelle comme une femme d\u00e9laiss\u00e9e et au c\u0153ur attrist\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme une \u00e9pouse de la jeunesse qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 r\u00e9pudi\u00e9e, dit ton Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.7","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.5","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.7","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:7","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Quelques instants je t\u2019avais abandonn\u00e9e,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais avec une grande affection je t\u2019accueillerai;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.8","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.6","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.8","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:8","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Dans un instant de col\u00e8re, je t\u2019avais un moment d\u00e9rob\u00e9 ma face,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais avec un amour \u00e9ternel j\u2019aurai compassion de toi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dit ton r\u00e9dempteur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.9","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.7","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.9","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:9","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Il en sera pour moi comme des eaux de No\u00e9:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    J\u2019avais jur\u00e9 que les eaux de No\u00e9 ne se r\u00e9pandraient plus sur la terre;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je jure de m\u00eame de ne plus m\u2019irriter contre toi<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et de ne plus te menacer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.10","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.8","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.10","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:10","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Quand les montagnes s\u2019\u00e9loigneraient,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Quand les collines chancelleraient,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mon amour ne s\u2019\u00e9loignera point de toi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et mon alliance de paix ne chancellera point,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qui a compassion de toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.11","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.9","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.11","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:11","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-17: cf. \u00c9s 60:17, etc. Ap 21:10, etc. Ro 8:31, 33, 37.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Malheureuse, battue de la temp\u00eate, et que nul ne console!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Voici, je garnirai tes pierres d\u2019antimoine,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et je te donnerai des fondements de saphir;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.10","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.12","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:12","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Je ferai tes cr\u00e9neaux de rubis,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tes portes d\u2019escarboucles,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et toute ton enceinte de pierres pr\u00e9cieuses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.13","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.11","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.13","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:13","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>\n    Tous tes fils seront disciples de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et grande sera la prosp\u00e9rit\u00e9 de tes fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.14","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.14","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:14","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Tu seras affermie par la justice;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Bannis l\u2019inqui\u00e9tude, car tu n\u2019as rien \u00e0 craindre,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et la frayeur, car elle n\u2019approchera pas de toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.15","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:15","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.13","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.15","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:15","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Si l\u2019on forme des complots, cela ne viendra pas de moi;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Quiconque se liguera contre toi tombera sous ton pouvoir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.16","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:16","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.14","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.16","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:16","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.054.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Voici, j\u2019ai cr\u00e9\u00e9 l\u2019ouvrier qui souffle le charbon au feu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et qui fabrique une arme par son travail;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais j\u2019ai cr\u00e9\u00e9 aussi le destructeur pour la briser.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.15","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:15","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.17","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:17","prev_osis_id":"Isa.054.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.055.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.54.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Toute arme forg\u00e9e contre toi sera sans effet;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et toute langue qui s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8vera en justice contre toi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu la condamneras.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tel est l\u2019h\u00e9ritage des serviteurs de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tel est le salut qui leur viendra de moi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.54","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.55.1","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 55:1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.55.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.54.16","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 54:16","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.54.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbd4a0689.69564058');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbd4a0689.69564058\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbd4a0689.69564058","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbd4a0689.